Install Cygwin64.
 * Disable virus protection
 * Obtain setup program from https://www.cygwin.com/setup-x86_64.exe
 * Run the setup program
 * Install into c:\cygwin64  [the default]
 * Put local packages in c:\Program Files\cygwin-local-packages
   (Don't do this for Cat's computer, though.)
 * Start out with a base installation:  install nothing extra
 * Run cmd.exe, then within it run:
    Desktop\setup-x86_64.exe -q -P wget,tar,qawk,bzip2,subversion,unzip,zip,automake,cvs,gcc-core,gcc-g++,git,make,mercurial,patch,subversion,emacs,emacs-el,m4,python3,libiconv,ca-certificates,curl,texlive-collection-latex,texlive-collection-latex-doc,texlive-collection-latexextra,texlive-collection-latexextra-doc,texlive-collection-latexrecommended,texlive-collection-latexrecommended-doc,xterm,w3m,wget,diffutils,dos2unix,ncurses,patchutils,time,unison2.48,w3m
I need to install gradle manually, it seems.

