# Run C:\cygwin\bin\ash.exe from Windows Command Shell:
export TEMP=/tmp
export TMP=/tmp
/bin/rebaseall

Follow the directions in ~/wisdom/setup/setup-linux-account

Make symbolic link to ~mernst and to ~mernst/sync (they are at C:\cygwin64) from Desktop.
It's critical to make the shortcut in place (via right-click in Windows
Explorer), then move it afterward.

Install hunspell:  ~/wisdom/building/build-hunspell

