For unistallation instructions (if I need to do a complete reinstall), see
  http://cygwin.com/faq/faq.html#faq.setup.uninstall-all
However, do not delete the entire Cygwin directory.  First synchronize with
Unison, and then move my home directory aside and put it back after the
install.  The reason is that an initial synchronization with Unison takes a
very long time.

